{
  "stem": "1282.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was supposed to get on the last ship because I was working with this organization.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dorhapunames ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anis ?] organization, that organized this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- they never wanted me to get on because I was fluent in Hungarian, I knew my way around, and I was able to deliver false certificates, gentile papers, to these people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which now there were not that many that were able to do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they always asked me to stay on, to stay on, to stay on a little longer, and I never got on any of the boats.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then it was too late and it was cut off, because by that time, Horthy resigned, the Arrow Cross took over, Eichmann came into Budapest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that-- that's when it started, the year where Raoul Wallenberg came to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we changed our policy and we started working through Raoul Wallenberg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Spent my nights in a printing shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started before Wallenberg, we really became strong when Wallenberg was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Wallenberg couldn't have done what he did by himself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had hundreds and hundreds of helpers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But mostly they were young kids like me, 15, 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew the city and our biggest job was if we got a hold of six passes-- six Schutz-Pass, Schutz-- what's that thing they call it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That Raoul Wallenberg's office issued, we copied it, we duplicated it, it looked very authentic, and we were able to give this out and-- and-- and distributed it to people that were not able to get it from the Wallenberg organization directly.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
